task.summary: Added LetterSplitter and LetterQuery functions to the DictionaryHandler
Added CompareBytes, a validation of the hashed passwords
Added the return true to CompareBytes
Added CheckWordsWithVeriation, this alters the dictionary word to try and hit as many veriations of passwords as possible

Now shows time stamp at end
also fixed a bug where the capitalized letter function didnt work
Added a ThreadHandler and refactored the code to handle Tasks. Made the split dictionary work as well. Though the program stops after loading in the passwords.txt
